  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/60cc24a69635e1656d65a580fb7ffe0a.avif?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=344 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/f2e734e218ad1dba94a0442ae0746b4f.avif?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Inspired by the old-style isometric arcade racing games, <strong>OverShoot Battle Race</strong> is an extremely fun racing game that brings back the emotion to play a battle racing game alone or with his friends</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/5df515cd25474ef3b757caa3df60b2f3.webp?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=41 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/adead4d8b45daccbff0d944c96157a51.poster.avif?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/adead4d8b45daccbff0d944c96157a51.webm?t=1748942465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/adead4d8b45daccbff0d944c96157a51.mp4?t=1748942465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Keep chasing your opponent until exploding it</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/c5899b90c28f53ec570be5eb36e95975.avif?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=73 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/fb8dad2f2ea7cbe1747717250c72d314.poster.avif?t=1748942465\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/fb8dad2f2ea7cbe1747717250c72d314.webm?t=1748942465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/fb8dad2f2ea7cbe1747717250c72d314.mp4?t=1748942465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Insane gameplay with lots and lots of explosions</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318280/extras/288762f1769654c82516e39f99302523.webp?t=1748942465\" width=80 height=31 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.